<collectionCode box="[894,932,1951,1977]" pageId="4" pageNumber="68">KT</collectionCode>
984) showed 36 bp (900/936 bp) differences. Morphologically, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Y. Feng, S. N. Zhang &amp; Z. Y. Liu" authorityYear="2022" box="[334,602,1987,2013]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Aigialaceae" genus="Fissuroma" kingdom="Fungi" order="Pleosporales" pageId="4" pageNumber="68" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="bambucicola">
<emphasis box="[334,602,1987,2013]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="68">Fissuroma bambucicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
